%div#help_develop_proposal
	%style
		:sass
			div#help_develop_proposal
				width: 505px
				li
					margin-bottom: .5em
			
	%h2 You can help develop a proposal
	%p Work together with your friends and community members to develop a community written and supported proposal for constructive change.
	%p Helping is easy and rewarding
	%ol
		%li 
			Select a proposal from the list on the left side of the
			= link_to 'home page', home_path
			and click the link that says 
			%b Help us make a difference
		%li You'll see the questions and talking points that make up the proposal
		%li Click one of the questions to see the worksheet where you can work with others to:
		%ul
			%li Discuss the question
			%li Rate the talking points
			%li Select up to 5 talking points you most prefer
			%li Discuss specific talking points
			%li Suggest a talking point
			%li Edit the talking points created by others
		%li This process of suggesting, discussing, revising, rating, and preferring helps us to think together
		%li Your participation will be convenient and productive with email notifications and the highlighting of new talking points and comments
	%p 
		Click the link that says 
		%b Help us make a difference
		under a proposal that interests you
		
	- if @member.first_name.nil?
		%h3 We need to know what you think!	
	- else
		%h3 #{@member.first_name}, we need to know what you think!	

	%p
		You can also watch our
		= link_to 'intro video', {},:rel=>'prettyPhoto', :href=>'http://vimeo.com/29348381', :title=>'2029 CivicEvolution Intro'
		or visit our
		#{link_to "visual help page", help_path, {:remote=>true}}

	%p 
		= link_to "Return to home page", home_path, {:class=>'cancel'}
		
	